      <title>5 takeaways from the 2025 elections. And, the shutdown now the longest in U.S. history</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/11/05/g-s1-96591/up-first-newsletter-election-day-takeaways-government-shutdown-trump-tariffs-israel-top-military-lawyer</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/11/05/g-s1-96591/up-first-newsletter-election-day-takeaways-government-shutdown-trump-tariffs-israel-top-military-lawyer</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.npr.org/2025/11/05/g-s1-96591/up-first-newsletter-election-day-takeaways-government-shutdown-trump-tariffs-israel-top-military-lawyer</guid>
